{"id":973480,"date":[{"year":1995,"month":2,"day":3}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"画刊","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"362","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我们走进春天","ftitle":"","authors":["田永昌"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天又开始被埋进昨天的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红梅枝头传出了春天的消息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花儿又慢慢地停止了飘落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山花儿娓娓地吐露着艳丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一粒种子又抢先睁开绿色眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一条小溪欢快地弹奏起绿色旋律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷又要轰隆隆地轰响着从天廷滚过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨淅沥沥地淋湿多情的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风又将吹拂书画家那智慧的额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔端泼洒出春天这一永恒的主题……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，春天，且莫说春天年年如期而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切的一切都是如此地熟悉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们张开双臂走进春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下的每一条道路都挑着沉甸甸地期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冀……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田永昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入10号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1995\\02\\9523040201.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>沈柔坚</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>春色(中国画)　沈柔坚</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入10号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1995\\02\\9523040202.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>霍允庆,霍建本</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>接福迎祥(年画)　霍允庆　霍建本</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入10号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1995\\02\\9523040203.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>李光启</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>如意　寿　李光启　篆刻</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入10号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1995\\02\\9523040204.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>董连宝</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>黄金、泥巴和……　(版画)　董连宝</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入10号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1995\\02\\9523040205.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","tex